&lt;p>Based on the following example rule, all invocations of the &lt;code>getComment&lt;/code> method in the &lt;code>org.apache.dubbo.samples.CommentService&lt;/code> service will be forwarded to a subset of addresses marked with &lt;code>region=Hangzhou&lt;/code>.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>标签路由规则</title><link>https://cn.dubbo.apache.org/en/overview/core-features/traffic/tag-rule/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://cn.dubbo.apache.org/en/overview/core-features/traffic/tag-rule/</guid><description/></item><item><title>脚本路由规则</title><link>https://cn.dubbo.apache.org/en/overview/core-features/traffic/script-rule/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://cn.dubbo.apache.org/en/overview/core-features/traffic/script-rule/</guid><description/></item><item><title>动态配置规则</title><link>https://cn.dubbo.apache.org/en/overview/core-features/traffic/configuration-rule/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://cn.dubbo.apache.org/en/overview/core-features/traffic/configuration-rule/</guid><description/></item><item><title>基于服务网格的路由规则</title><link>https://cn.dubbo.apache.org/en/overview/core-features/traffic/mesh-rule/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://cn.dubbo.apache.org/en/overview/core-features/traffic/mesh-rule/</guid><description/></item></channel></rss>